R^{4}
X=X^{1}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{1}}
Y=Y^{1}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{1}}
N(X,Y)
N
X=X^{1}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{1}}+X^{2}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{2}}+X^{3}\frac{\partial}{\partial y^{1}}+X^{4}\frac{\partial}{\partial y^{2}}
Y=Y^{1}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{1}}+Y^{2}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{2}}+Y^{3}\frac{\partial}{\partial y^{1}}+Y^{4}\frac{\partial}{\partial y^{2}}
